                    "SS2_CYBORG2_UTILITY_TELEPORT_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003eTÃ©lÃ©portez\u003c/style\u003e-vous vers votre \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003epoint de distorsion\u003c/style\u003e.",
