                    "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_SECONDARY_BEAM_DESCRIPTION":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eEntaille\u003c/style\u003e. LibÃ¨re un faisceau d\u0027Ã©pÃ©e \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003eperÃ§ant\u003c/style\u003e infligeant \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e400% de dÃ©gÃ¢ts\u003c/style\u003e.",
