                    "SS2_ITEM_VOIDROCK_DESC":  "Devenez la proie des \u003cstyle=cDeath\u003eSurvivants NÃ©mÃ©sis\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_DIFFICULTY_TYPHOON_DESC":  "DÃ©fi maximum. Le monde est un cauchemar, et la survie n\u0027est qu\u0027une illusion. Personne n\u0027a ce qu\u0027il faut.\u003cstyle=cStack\u003e\n\n\u003eRÃ©gÃ©nÃ©ration de santÃ© du joueur : \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003e-40%\u003c/style\u003e\n\u003eÃ‰chelle de difficultÃ© : \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003e+75%\u003c/style\u003e\n\u003eLimite de spawn de monstres : \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003e+100%\u003c/style\u003e\n\u003eTaux de spawn de monstres : \u003cstyle=cIsHealth\u003e+25%\u003c/style\u003e\n\u003eRÃ©compenses d\u0027Or et d\u0027XP : \u003cstyle=cisHealth\u003e-20%\u003c/style\u003e",
                    "SS2_ITEM_FORK_PICKUP":  "Infligez davantage de dÃ©gÃ¢ts.",
