                    "SS2_ITEM_SHACKLEDLAMP_DESC":  "Toutes les \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e5 utilisations de la compÃ©tence principale\u003c/style\u003e, tirez un projectile hantÃ© infligeant des dÃ©gÃ¢ts de base de \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e200%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+200% par accumulation)\u003c/style\u003e.",
                    "SS2_NEMEXECUTIONER_PRIMARY_DESCRIPTION":  "chaÃ®ne d\u0027Ã©clairs en boule",
